@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Get Context (Retrieve Relevant Chunks)

skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam activity {
    BackgroundColor SkyBlue
    BorderColor #0066CC
}

|User|
start
:Request context retrieval\n(Query text + Project ID\n+ Number of results);

|System|
:Receive context request;
:Expand query\n(Add related terms);
note right: Query expansion

:Generate query embedding\n(OpenAI text-embedding-3-small);

:Search in Supabase\n(Cosine similarity search);
note right: Finding similar chunks

:Get top k chunks\n(sorted by relevance score);

:Calculate relevance\n(relevance = 1 - similarity score);

:Transform results\n(Add metadata);

:Return context chunks\nwith relevance scores;

|User|
:Receive context chunks\n(Array of relevant text chunks);
:Use chunks for analysis\nor display;
stop

@enduml
